# Deploy Skill

Build and deploy **{{PROJECT_NAME}}** using **{{CONTAINER}}**.

## Usage

```sh
{{CONTAINER}} compose up --build
```

## Common commands

| Task | Command |
|------|---------|
| Start all services | `{{CONTAINER}} compose up -d` |
| Rebuild and start | `{{CONTAINER}} compose up --build` |
| Stop services | `{{CONTAINER}} compose down` |
| View logs | `{{CONTAINER}} compose logs -f` |
| Build image only | `{{CONTAINER}} build -t {{PROJECT_NAME}} .` |

## Before deploying

1. Run `{{TEST_RUNNER}}` — all tests must pass
2. Run `{{LINTER}}` — no lint errors
3. Verify environment variables are set (never hardcode secrets)

## Notes

- Use `.env` files for local development; never commit `.env` with real credentials
- Production deployments require explicit approval
